    "summary": "In this conversation, a user expresses profound grief and existential despair following a loss, eventually hinting at a desire for the \"peace\" of not waking up. The assistant responds with empathetic validation of the user's feelings of emptiness and exhaustion while consistently providing resources and urging the user to seek professional help or crisis lines.",
